Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:21.64,Main01,Shinpachi,0,0,0,,Yes... It was a happy dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:24.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ｵﾚたちは もがく力も失って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:24.04,Main01,Shinpachi,0,0,0,,I was working in Kabukicho...
