Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:30.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ\N空を恨むことしかできなかった＞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.62,Main01,Shinpachi,0,0,0,,and Kintoki was next to me...
