Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.51,Main01,Kagura,0,0,0,,I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.98,Main01,Gintoki,0,0,0,,You already said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:29.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,眠れないなら眠くなるまで\N寝なきゃいいだろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.24,Main01,Gintoki,0,0,0,,If you can't fall asleep, stay up until you're sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.47,Main01,Gintoki,0,0,0,,You're so annoying.
