Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寝かせろよ 私を｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.46,Main01,Kagura,0,0,0,,Put me to sleep.
