Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.37,Main01,Kagura,0,0,0,,This is no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:49.65,Main01,Kagura,0,0,0,,I don't feel sleepy at all.
