Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.27,Main01,Gintoki,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to switch with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.61,Main01,Kagura,0,0,0,,That futon looks more comfortable to sleep on.
